About Lycamobile Australia

Buy a Lycamobile recharge on Recharge.com so you will never run out of minutes or texts. It only takes a few taps! We know how frustrating it is not to have enough credit. Just when you need to call your Mom, text your friend or look something up online. With Recharge.com, you can top up Lycamobile plans immediately. You'll be back on your phone before you know it with Lycamobile top-up!
To recharge Lycamobile prepaid plans, simply select the amount you need and enter your phone number. Your payment is fast and easy using PayPal, VISA, Mastercard, credit card/debit card, or more than 23 other safe and secure payment methods. Your Lycamobile balance will be topped up immediately when the payment is complete! We will send the Lycamobile top-up code to the email inserted, with instructions on how to redeem the code.

  • Telstra Recharge
